snippet.title: stanfordonline
snippet.description: Stanford Online is Stanford’s online learning provider, offering learners access to Stanford’s extended education and lifelong learning opportunities. Our robust catalog of credit-bearing, professional, and free and open content provides a variety of ways to expand your learning, advance your career, and enhance your life. Stanford Online is operated and managed by the Stanford Center for Professional Development, a leader in online and extended education.
